This paper is about a machine learning system that covers the entire data science lifecycle, from data integration to serving. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Databases (cs.DB) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the system architecture and design decisions, which suggests that it may also belong to the Software Engineering (cs.SE) and Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC) sub-categories. Finally, the paper mentions the use of declarative languages and R-like syntax, which is a common feature in Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) research.
